    "plan_content": "## Implementation Plan: Stepper Compound Component\n\nHere's what I'll create — **2 new files** + **2 registry amendments**, no existing components touched.\n\n---\n\n### Architecture\nFollows the **`carousel.tsx` context pattern** (not Radix-wrapper). Two layers of context:\n\n- **`StepperContext`** — provides `activeStep` + `orientation` to all descendants\n- **`StepperItemContext`** — provides `step` + derived `state` (`\"completed\" | \"active\" | \"pending\"`) within each item\n- **`cva`** drives `StepperTrigger`'s 3 visual states (pending = outlined circle, active/completed = filled primary color)\n\n---\n\n### File 1: `ui/stepper.tsx` — 7 named exports\n\n| Export | Element | Key behavior |\n|---|---|---|\n| `Stepper` | `<div>` | Context provider. Props: `activeStep` (required), `orientation` (default `\"horizontal\"`) |\n| `StepperItem` | `<div>` | Derives `state` from context, provides `StepperItemContext`. Props: `step: number` |\n| `StepperTrigger` | `<button>` | Reads `step`/`state` from item context, uses `cva` for styling. Renders `{children ?? step}` |\n| `StepperTitle` | `<p>` | `text-sm font-medium` |\n| `StepperDescription` | `<p>` | `text-xs text-muted-foreground` |\n| `StepperSeparator` | `<div>` | Reads `orientation` + `state` from contexts. Highlights `bg-primary` when parent step is completed |\n| `StepperContent` | `<div>` | Returns `null` when `step !== activeStep` |\n\n---\n\n### File 2: `examples/stepper-demo.tsx`\n3-step horizontal stepper (\"Account\" → \"Profile\" → \"Complete\") with `useState` for `activeStep`. Each `StepperItem` contains `StepperTrigger`, `StepperTitle`, `StepperDescription`, and `StepperSeparator` (except the last step). `StepperContent` panels below, Next/Previous buttons to navigate.\n\n---\n\n### Registry Amendments\n- **`ui/_registry.ts`**: Insert `\"stepper\"` entry (with `class-variance-authority` dependency) between `\"spinner\"` and `\"switch\"` entries (~line 563)\n- **`examples/_registry.ts`**: Insert `\"stepper-demo\"` entry (with `registryDependencies: [\"stepper\"]`) between `\"spinner-item\"` and `\"switch-demo\"` entries (~line 2124)",
